## Bundled data attribution

The bundled SQLite database (`src-tauri/resources/medbill_v1.sqlite`) is
derived from public-domain U.S. federal sources:

- **CMS MS-DRG Definitions Manual v43.0** (FY 2026) — Centers for Medicare
  & Medicaid Services. Public domain.
- **CMS IPPS FY 2026 Final Rule Table 5** (DRG relative weights, GMLOS,
  AMLOS) — CMS. Public domain.
- **Place of Service code set** — CMS. Public domain.
- **HCPCS Level II modifier set (alpha-numeric only)** — CMS. Public domain.

AMA CPT codes and CPT modifiers are excluded by design — they are not
in the public domain and are not redistributed by this software.

